<span id="v.iv.ii-p6"></span>This treatise was written about 400 <span
class="c11"><span id="v.iv.ii-p6.1"></span>A.D.</span>  Concerning it
Aug. in *Retract*. Book II. c. xviii., says:  I have written seven books
on Baptism against the Donatists, who strive to defend themselves by the
authority of the most blessed bishop and martyr Cyprian; in which I show
that nothing is so effectual for the refutation of the Donatists, and
for shutting their mouths directly from upholding their schism against
the Catholic Church, as the letters and act of Cyprian.

